summary.para: This class is available in Office 2010 and above.
When the object is serialized out as xml, it's qualified name is a14:hiddenLine.

remarks.format:
## Remarks *2.3.23 hiddenLine*
*Target namespace:* http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/drawing/2010/main
A *CT_LineProperties* element ([ISO/IEC-29500-1] section A.4.1) that stores the line information of an object when the line fill has been set to invisible. If line fill has been set to visible this element is ignored.
The following W3C XML Schema ([XMLSCHEMA1] section 2.1) fragment specifies the contents of this element.
*\<xsd:element name="hiddenLine" type="a:CT_LineProperties"/>*
See section 5.1 for the full W3C XML Schema ([XMLSCHEMA1] section 2.1).
